{"tid":1781899,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"有無人俾人炒都唔驚？咁就嚟加入先行者啦！","createTime":"2019-12-13T13:40:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-13T17:52:23.000Z","uid":89974,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"dda7755ae1d9b0b655befe16daf3e22851cfc8bd","tid":1781899,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T13:40:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">和理非唔係廢物，唔係剩係可以遊行捐錢！<br />\n<br />\n誠招所有被炒都唔驚嘅行動派！誠招所有被炒都唔驚嘅行動派！誠招所有被炒都唔驚嘅行動派！<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6qYyK1p89nU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D6qYyK1p89nU&d=ZRuO0gn2PDb4CPS%2BM%2Fpj6liy1AgKJyIubMvfhItfpFI%3D&h=e6a58b01\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6qYyK1p89nU</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GmkYKrIYcC8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DGmkYKrIYcC8&d=ZRuO0gn2PDb4CPS%2BM%2Fpj6liy1AgKJyIubMvfhItfpFI%3D&h=af9e756c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GmkYKrIYcC8</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">前言：</span><br />\n<br />\n我地係<span style=\"color: red;\">先行者</span>，一班唔怕被解僱，願意為社會出多一份力既人。<br />\n<br />\n極權步步進逼，由解放軍出動，二噁英毒氣滿佈，到以武力攻擊校園，以屠殺為目標。雖然近期我們先後贏得區選，並獲人權法案簽署，然而我們距離五大訴求，以及清算警隊仍然有一段距離。同時，中共將會重新審視對香港的形勢，更劇烈的打壓將會重臨。今日再唔反抗，我們將會迎來最悲慘既結局---新疆般既種族清洗。<span style=\"color: violet;\">雖然市面看似平靜，但警隊其實暗中仍然繼續行動，為的就是趕盡殺絕所有手足。</span><br />\n<br />\n因此，我正式呼籲各位<span style=\"color: brown;\">無負擔/敢於犧牲</span>的手足參與「罷工宣言」行動，透過遞信俾老細/同事，甚至係工司群組內發放文宣，去正式宣佈無限期罷工，為其他仲有負擔既人做一個榜樣。<br />\n<br />\n咁樣做，除咗可以打破囚徒困境(因為已知有&quot;1&quot;個人肯罷)，亦可以令香港經濟呢個緊密既齒輪鬆脫。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">一個人既罷工並非如大家想像中咁無用：</span><br />\n香港既高物價高薪金令人手長期緊張，一個人既罷工會令整間公司運作減緩，公司運作放緩就會令其生意既合作夥伴受到影響；一環扣一環下，社會就會漸漸癱瘓。唔少人嘅職位雖然低但係對公司而言不可或缺。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0ULa6qr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0ULa6qr.png&h=5f237c9d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/15mhMqr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F15mhMqr.png&h=3aaf90c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/isWxAiN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FisWxAiN.png&h=bc3b576e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iFhg1YN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiFhg1YN.png&h=25a6d560&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r81YvR7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr81YvR7.png&h=dadcaaed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DLVeODN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDLVeODN.png&h=751cf713&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P4hprqs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP4hprqs.png&h=2f2faca7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LuJDvR7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLuJDvR7.png&h=708ae63a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1WKjfiN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1WKjfiN.png&h=89a76678&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SquCMqt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSquCMqt.png&h=43eeba67&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">有負擔嘅手足，請以按章工作，拒絕OT作為表態。<br />\n就算你唔為咗手足，為咗自己健康都應該唔好OT啦，仲要無補水OT<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">點做更有效？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n請做足以下四步行動，令你嘅罷工更加有效：<br />\n1.發送文宣(whatsapp/email/打印)俾老細同事，宣佈你要罷工<br />\n2.嘗試與同事傾一傾而家處境有幾嚴峻，盡量說服佢地罷工<br />\n3.係社交媒體同朋友圈子內不停發佈，推post，務求令更多人知道呢件事<br />\n4.加入我地一齊宣傳<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RNqFH1B.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRNqFH1B.jpg&h=8a3d6e91&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3BNpqeX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3BNpqeX.jpg&h=f1140574&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HofnbUW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHofnbUW.jpg&h=79240c09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MYcg0Oh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMYcg0Oh.jpg&h=6117c648&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">得我罷咪變咗Condom？</span></span><br />\n呢個問題就要問手足你，到底願唔願意冒風險去嘗試營造一場公司罷工，定係下下都要等人，等工會帶？<br />\n前線手足有幾多人仲可以等咁耐？口講前線唔係Condom但係自己一啲犧牲都唔做？<br />\n<span style=\"color: maroon;\">只要多一個人全職投入抗爭，呢場抗爭就多一分勝算</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n請大家按自己能力入群！同時我們亦更加容易聯合到相同處境既人士！<br />\n1.第一梯隊：如果你願意做罷工敢炒隊，請去呢度：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/353CbNN\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F353CbNN&d=ZRuO0gn2PDb4CPS%2BM%2Fpj6liy1AgKJyIubMvfhItfpFI%3D&h=96856fd1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/353CbNN</a><br />\n2.第二梯隊：如果你公司有人做敢炒隊就會跟住罷工，請入呢度︰<a href=\"https://bit.ly/37bMbXd\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F37bMbXd&d=ZRuO0gn2PDb4CPS%2BM%2Fpj6liy1AgKJyIubMvfhItfpFI%3D&h=5ee86cc5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/37bMbXd</a><br />\n4.如果真係有好多人罷工/要有工會先罷工請入呢度︰<a href=\"http://t.me/hkonstrike\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkonstrike&d=ZRuO0gn2PDb4CPS%2BM%2Fpj6liy1AgKJyIubMvfhItfpFI%3D&h=bcbb4adb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/hkonstrike</a><br />\n5.如果你想得知最新消息請去公海︰<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2rHLbJV\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2rHLbJV&d=ZRuO0gn2PDb4CPS%2BM%2Fpj6liy1AgKJyIubMvfhItfpFI%3D&h=57482e08\" data-a